1.What is http?
It stands for Hypertext tranfer protocol
It is a protocol used for transmitting data over the internet. Http defines how clients and servers communicate with each other and how requests and responses should be formatted and 
transmitted . It is the foundation of data communication for the world wide web or the internet.

